opological edge states are\nhighly subradiant with extremely low decay rates, which therefore offer an\nappealing route for controlling the emission of external quantum emitters and\nachieving high-fidelity quantum state storage.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2020 03:53:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2021 07:12:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
