nDSA respectively. Deployment of XReg on DSA in Bing resulted in a relative gain\nof 27% in query coverage. XReg's source code can be downloaded from\nhttp://manikvarma.org/code/XReg/download.html.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2020 10:56:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jan 2020 02:34:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2020 10:46:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-22"}
