ng down of the spin dynamics or by\nstrengthening the pyrochlore phase by suitable substitution in the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2020 11:19:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2020 06:25:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
